Definition wand {A} {JA: Join A} (p q:pred A) := fun y => forall x z, join x y z -> p x -> q z.
Notation "P '|--' Q" := (derives P Q) (at level 80, no associativity).

Infix "||" := orp (at level 50, left associativity) : pred.
